Plot: Qui-Gon Jinn's past is not at rest. How can he forge a bond with young Obi-Wan Kenobi while he is haunted by the betrayal of his first apprentice--Xanatos? Xanatos was also a promising student . . . until the dark side of the Force intervened. Qui-Gon thought he was gone forever. But now Xanatos is back. And he wants revenge.
Characters: Qui-Gon Jinn, Obi-Wan Kenobi, Xanatos, Si Treemba, Guerra Derida, Clat'Ha, RonTha, SonTag, VeerTa
